Cory Hardrict https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cory_Hardrict 0 Cory Hardrict (born November 9, 1979) is an American actor. He has appeared in film and television since the late 1990s. He was an executive producer for the 2012 film The Watch. Cory_Hardrict ( born November_9_,_1979 ) is an_American_actor . He has_appeared in film_and_television since the_late_1990s .
